channel.title: [Delta]objects that are not suppose to be objects/not be there?
channel.description: I been working on remaking lumby, yet I get so mad because there are random spots of godwars objects around my server, along with some other items like lightsaber. I spent +2hr looking around my client for the models and nothing. I deleted all the anims besides the godsword stance and nothing. Btw I deleted the lightsaber model, yet it still shows up. The godwars objects act like random ground spots, fences, and some gates. I have no clue what to do and would like some help out..thanks
